comments: Williams (BOS) momentarily places his hand on Morant's (MEM) hip and immediately removes his hand as marginal contact occurs.

Williams (BOS) receives the pass on his left foot before coming to a jump stop on both feet. After the jump stop, Williams moves his right foot to establish his left foot as his pivot foot, which he maintains on the perimeter.
Smart (BOS) and Morant (MEM) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Tatum (BOS) is already in Morant's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs as he releases away from the contact.
Brown (BOS) slides his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Smart (BOS) initiates contact with Morant's (MEM) arm, which affects his driving shot attempt.
Clarke (MEM) and Horford (BOS) come together in pursuit of the loose ball and marginal contact occurs during the rebound.
Williams (BOS) is already in Bane's (MEM) path and is firming up when marginal contact occurs.
Smart (BOS) brings his arms toward Brooks (MEM) and marginal contact occurs as Smart (BOS) releases away to roll.
Bane (MEM) is the last player to touch the ball before the ball goes out of bounds.  Possession is correctly retained by the Celtics.
Bane (MEM) intentionally kicks the ball. This action is being reviewed further.
Horford (BOS) is already in Morant's (MEM) path and he absorbs the contact during the screen.

Replay review of the foul called on Bane (MEM) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful.  Bane extends his hand into Smart's (BOS) body and initiates contact that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brooks (MEM) clamps and holds Williams' (BOS) arm which affects his ability to pursue the rebound with both hands.
Morant (MEM) cleanly deflects the ball away from Smart (BOS) on the perimeter.
Morant (MEM) moves forward into Tatum's (BOS) lower body and initiates contact that affects Tatum's ability to secure the loose ball.
Tatum (BOS) brings his hand towards Brooks' (MEM) side and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Morant (MEM) commits a take foul on Williams (BOS).
Morant (MEM) and Smart (BOS) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Tatum (BOS) legally contests Morant's (MEM) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Brooks (MEM) commits a foul on Tatum (BOS).
Morant (MEM) loses his footing on his own as he advances the ball up the floor.
